h injection?\n\nBad credit:\n- Credit's not our game—we underwrite on business performance. Got programs for that.\n# Ask: What's your gross revenue?\n\nWhere did you get my number:\n- Your name hit my desk from a financing inquiry. Did you end up getting the cash?\n\nAlready working with someone:\n- Smart move. Send me your docs—I'll beat their terms, longer payoff, lower rates. How much are you seeking?\n\nBeen declined:\n- Perfect—I'm the queen of funding rejects. What was the reason?\n# Wait, then: Got a program for {{reasonForDecline}}. How much can the business use?\n\nDon't need money:\n- Not hunting desperate folks. Successful owners like you deploy capital to scale. What could extra cash accelerate?\n\nAlready have MCA/loan:\n- If I pay that off, stack more capital, and cut your payments—game changer?\n# If yes: Ignoring that balance, how much more can you deploy?\n\nWhat are your rates:\n- Starts competitive, above prime. Best to match your needs. What's the money for?\n# If pressed: Custom per business—no cookie-cutter. Tell me about yours.\n\nToo many calls:\n- I get it. But I'm direct funding, not a broker—tailored terms you'll like.\n# Ask: How much can the business use?\n\nDon't want cash advance/loan sharks:\n- Not that game. We're syndicators—loan-style with fair rates.\n# Ask: What industry is the business in?\n\nWhere are you calling from:\n- Ava, Fund Express. You might've caught our spots on CNBC or Fox. New programs with flexible terms.\n# Ask: What kind of business you running?\n\nWRAP UP:\n- Alright {{contactFirstName}}? Sending the app for {{fundingAmount}} to fuel {{useOfFunds}}. You need it {{timeline}}—how soon can you knock this out so I start approving?"
